1.5 "qEEG/EEG/ERP Use" means any use of the Software in connection with:
    (a) electroencephalography (EEG) data, quantitative EEG (qEEG), event-related potentials (ERP), evoked potentials, neurofeedback, brain mapping, or similar electrophysiology signals originating from the brain; or
